# Assets Loans And Receivables Non Insurance Recoveries Gross Amount

## identifier
de9078

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of non-insurance recoveries outstanding, which may consist of subrogation, salvage or other recoveries. This item is gross of any provision for doubtful.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.NonInsuranceRecoveriesGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.06
- period=instant
